Package com.gh.bmd.rfc.android.iterator

Package containing classes defining the iterable wrapping the Android sparse collection objects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BooleanSparseIterable
    This interface extends the ElementSparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling boolean elements.
    ElementSparseIterable<E>
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling serialization of the elements to lists and arrays.
    IntSparseIterable
    This interface extends the ElementSparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling int elements.
    LongSparseArrayIterable<V>
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling LongSparseArrayEntry elements.
    LongSparseIterable
    This interface extends the ElementSparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling long elements.
    SimpleArrayMapIterable<K,V>
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling SimpleArrayMapEntry elements.
    SparseArrayCompatIterable<V>
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling SparseArrayEntry elements.
    SparseArrayIterable<V>
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling SparseArrayEntry elements.
    SparseBooleanArrayIterable
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling SparseBooleanArrayEntry elements.
    SparseIntArrayIterable
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling SparseIntArrayEntry elements.
    SparseIterable<E>
    This interface defines the base functionalities of an Iterable wrapping an Android sparse collection, such as SparseArray and SparseArrayCompat.
    SparseIterable.Action<E>
    This interface defines an action to be applied to the iterable elements.
    SparseIterable.Condition<E>
    This interface defines a condition to be applied to the iterable elements.
    SparseLongArrayIterable
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling SparseLongArrayEntry elements.
    SupportLongSparseArrayIterable<V>
    This interface extends the SparseIterable one by adding specific methods handling LongSparseArrayEntry elements.
